{"article_id":"7GK2mPl8eEywyjD1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump named the European Union , Russia and China as \" foes \" of the U.S.","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"as he heads into a Monday meeting with Russian President Vladimir Putin in Helsinki , Finland .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"\" I think","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"we have a lot of foes .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"I think","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the European Union is a foe ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"what they do to us in trade , \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Trump told CBS News in excerpts of an interview","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"released Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" Now you wouldn ' t think of the European Union ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but they ' re a foe .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Russia is foe in certain respects .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"China is a foe economically ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"certainly they are a foe . \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" But that doesn ' t mean they are bad , \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"\" It doesn ' t mean anything .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"It means that they are competitive .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"They want to do well ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and we want to do well . \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Interviewer Jeff Glor said","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"people might be surprised to hear","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Trump label the EU a foe ahead of China or Russia .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"he looks at them al ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"l but the EU is \" difficult . \"","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"\" In a trade sense , they ' ve really taken advantage of us","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"and many of those countries are in NATO","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and they weren ' t paying their bills , \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"the president said .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"Mr. Trump said last week","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"that NATO member-countries agreed to up their spending on defense after a summit of leaders of the countries in Brussels ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"though other leaders later disputed Mr. Trump ' s assertion .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"In the interview , Mr. Trump also criticized a recent deal","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Germany struck with Russia on the planned Nord Stream 2 pipeline project ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"calling it \" not fair . \"","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"\" You ' re supposed to be fighting for someone","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and then that someone gives billions of dollars to the one","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"you ' re ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"you know ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"guarding against .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"it ' s ridiculous ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"so I let that be known also this time , \"","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"he president said .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"He said","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"there ' s \" a lot of anger \"","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"that Germany is paying Russia \" billions \" of dollars .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"\" I also think","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"it ' s a very bad thing for Germany , \"","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"\" Because it ' s like ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"what are they waving , a white flag ? \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":105,"left":72,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":54,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":55,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":59,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"at